-- Xstrata and Anglo Platinum Facing Secondary Strikes, Union Says
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-10-27T09:03:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-27/xstrata-and-anglo-platinum-facing-secondary-strikes-union-says.html
Xstrata Plc and Anglo Platinum Ltd.
are facing a secondary strike in support of workers at their
Mototolo mine joint-venture in South Africa, the National Union
of Mineworkers said.  Workers at the Thorncliffe Mine and Lydenburg works have
this week joined the action, the labor union said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  